act_type': 'label'}, {'type': 'followup', 'email': 'primeedmrecords@hotmail.com', 'name': 'Prime EDM Records', 'subject': 'Re: None', 'body': "Hey, wanted to check in on the beats I sent over last week—sometimes things get buried in the inbox. Quick question: what's your team's workflow for discovering new producers right now? Would love to know how you typically work with fresh talent.\n\nRobert-Jan\nrobertjanmastenbroek.com | https://instagram.com/robertjanmastenbroek", 'thread_url': None, 'contact_type': 'label'}, {'type': 'followup', 'email': 'pcrrecords.official@gmail.com', 'name': 'PCR Records', 'subject': 'Re: None', 'body': "Hey, wanted to check back on my previous message. I've been exploring some exciting sonic directions—have you noticed any trends in releases catching your ear at PCR? Would love to hear what's resonating with you.\n\nCheers,\nRobert-Jan\nrobertjanmastenbroek.com | https://instagram.com/robertjanmastenbroek", 'thread_url': None, 'contact_type': 'label'}, {'type': 'followup', 'email': 'demos@yhvmusic.group', 'name': 'YHV Records', 'subject': 'Re: None', 'body': "Hey,\n\nThrew something your way a few weeks back about working together. What kind of electronic production are you actively pushing right now? Think my Bible-inspired techno could be a solid fit with what you're building.\n\nKeen to chat more.\n\nRobert-Jan\nrobertjanmastenbroek.com | https://instagram.com/robertjanmastenbroek", 'thread_url': None, 'contact_type': 'label'}, {'type': 'followup', 'email': 'info@deephousecats.com', 'name': 'Deep House Cats SA', 'subject': 'Re: None', 'body': "Hey,\n\nWanted to circle back on my previous message about potentially working together. I've got fresh tracks that align with your deep house aesthetic, and I'm curious—are you currently reviewing new submissions, or is there a better time to connect?\n\nRobert-Jan\nrobertjanmastenbroek.com | https://instagram.com/robertjanmastenbroek", 'thread_url': None, 'contact_type': 'label'}, {'type': 'f